======================================================================
GLMY PATH HOMOLOGY v2 — VALIDATION
======================================================================

--- Directed 3-cycle C_3 ---
  Expected: β = [1, 1, 0] (1 component, 1 directed hole)
  Got: β = [1, 1, 0]

--- Directed path P_3 ---
  Expected: β = [1, 0, 0] (connected, contractible)
  Got: β = [1, 0, 0]

--- Transitive tournament T_3: 0->1, 0->2, 1->2 ---
  This is an acyclic tournament. Expected: β_1 = 0 (no directed holes)
  Got: β = [1, 0, 0]

--- 3-cycle tournament: 0->1, 1->2, 2->0 ---
  Got: β = [1, 1, 0]

--- Directed 4-cycle C_4 ---
  Expected: β = [1, 1, 0, 0]
  Got: β = [1, 1, 0, 0]

--- Complete bidirected K_3 ---
  Got: β = [1, 0, 2]

--- 0->1, vertex 2 isolated ---
  Got: β = [2, 0, 0]
  Expected: β_0 = 3 or 2 (depends on convention)


